import React from "react"

const InputField = props => (
  <form>
    <label htmlFor="titleField">
      Todo:
      <input
        id="titleField"
        type="text"
        value={props.title}
        onChange={e => props.handleInputChange(e)}
      />
    </label>
    <button type="submit">Submit</button>
  </form>
)

export default InputField
